OL,5, A care agency boss has described the   
OL,6, NHS as "a joke" after a disabled man   
OL,7, was forced to wait for 48 hours in A&E.
OL,9,FOne of David Williams' clients, who has
OL,10,Fsevere epilepsy, had been taken to the 
OL,11,FGrange Hospital near Cwmbran, Torfaen, 
OL,12,Fcomplaining of chest pain.             
OL,14,FMr Williams said he had to wait in a   
OL,15,Fchair with no food for 36 hours.       
OL,17,FAneurin Bevan health board said delayed
OL,18,Fhospital discharges and winter viruses 
OL,19,Fhad led to longer waits at A&E.        
